  "texts": [
    "Numerical values have been assigned to the coefficients in the proportionality test to enhance clarity, but these coefficients can also be compared through non-numerical preferences or magnitudes, such as the Paretian superiority illustrated in (Sartor, 2018).",
    "On a different note, we cannot ignore the role that EU institutions-and, in particular, the role that the EU Court of Justice-shall play in preserving the constitutional framework of the Union and the untouchable core of the EU legal order, which include its fundamental values and rights.",
    "This is why in the next section, we shall discuss the allocation of competences and roles in scenario building and proportionality assessments.",
    "6 Using the Semi-Quantitative Risk Approach: Three Applications Under the AIA",
    "We illustrate three potential uses of this semi-quantitative risk framework under the AIA."
